"{\"uid\": \"thenews.com.pk-latest-1219161-tom-cruise-skydives-into-olympic-history-during-paris-2024-closing-ceremony\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Tom Cruise brought his signature flair to the 2024 Paris Olympics closing ceremony that symbolised the transition to Los Angeles for the 2028 Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 10, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 117, \"end\": 128, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999962647053, \"rank\": 3.679310620336146e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a daring skydiving stunt on Sunday, August 11, the action star, 62, descended from the top of Stade de France before landing gracefully on the field.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 247, \"end\": 262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was greeted by athletes and a rocking performance by H.E.R, who had just delivered the national anthem.\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After receiving the Olympic flag from Los Angeles Mayor Karen Bass and gold-medal-winning gymnast Simone Biles, Cruise strapped it to the back of a motorcycle and sped off.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 583, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 449, \"end\": 460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999962647053, \"rank\": 3.679310620336146e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}, {\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karen Bass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karen_Bass\"}, {\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheMission: Impossibleactor then embarked on a cinematic journey to Hollywood via a pre-recorded video.\", \"from\": 585, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 653, \"end\": 662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999059120954, \"rank\": 9.404320687038207e-08, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The video showed Cruise weaving through the roads of Paris, driving past landmarks like the Eiffel Tower, and boarding a plane bound for Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 742, \"end\": 747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996844053, \"rank\": 3.155895480131324e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 826, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999962647053, \"rank\": 3.679310620336146e-09, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once in the City of Angels, Cruise skydived towards the iconic Hollywood sign, replacing its \\\"O\\\"s into Olympic rings before handing the flag off to Olympic cyclist Kate Courtney.\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hollywood sign\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hollywood_Sign\"}, {\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Courtney_(cyclist)\", \"score\": 0.9999981956923782, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kate Courtney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Courtney_(cyclist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Courtney_(cyclist)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Courtney, along with Olympians Michael Johnson and Jagger Eaton, continued the journey through L.A., eventually arriving at a Red Hot Chili Peppers concert on Venice Beach.\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1020, \"end\": 1028, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courtney_Love\", \"score\": 0.9999999999022293, \"rank\": 9.779884733160629e-11, \"text\": \"Courtney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courtney_Love\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Courtney_Love\"}, {\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Johnson_(sprinter)\", \"score\": 0.6562406956374156, \"rank\": 0.27532889874352734, \"text\": \"Michael Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627